Class DataColumn

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.comp3111.DataColumn
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DataColumn
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    DataColumn - A column of data. This class will be used by DataTable. It stores the data values (data) and the its type (typeName). String constants of type name are defined in DataType.
    Author:
    cspeter
